com.hcl.domino.data

Interface DocumentSelection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<Integer>, DominoClientDescendant, IAdaptable, IDTable, Iterable<Integer>, Set<Integer>

    public interface DocumentSelection
extends IDTable, DominoClientDescendant
    Subclass of IDTable to select data, design or admin documents from an NSF.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  DocumentSelection.SelectionType
      The available document types that can be selected via select(Collection) and select(SelectionType...).
